Class MinHypothesisStep

mmj.gmff.MinHypothesisStep
public class MinHypothesisStep extends MinProofStepStmt
Hypothesis step on a MinProofWorksheet.

Note: at this time GMFF does not need to know whether a proof step is an hypothesis or a derivation step, but MinHypothesisStep and MinDerivationStep are provided for completeness and future possibilities :-)

      w - the MinProofworksheet object which contains the proof step.
